Program: The Documentary
Title: Linda For Congress
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03gpj0g
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 8 Feb 2016
The road to the White House requires stamina and plenty of money. Economist and US Citizen, Linda Yueh, makes a hypothetical run for Congress in the 5th district of Virgina, to find out why it costs so much money to run for office and the increasing importance of the internet in a campaign. On the way she gathers a campaign team, meets her voters and learns about the importance of pizza in politics. Show less